race.comment: BLACKPOOL TRIP (1) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at his last four runs. Last time finished 2nd in a Grade 5 on October 20 over 278m at this track behind Fisherman's Wish beaten 4 lengths (16.29). Ready to find winning form. MISS CHIRPY (3) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at Hobart over 340m behind Push The Button (19.83) in a Grade 4. Placed at her previous run. Has ability and can measure up. LIFE IS YOURS (5) solid chance again. Something for the Multiples: DAD'S TARPIA (4)
